text: Pleasant eatery that offers Vietnamese and Western snacks and bites.

Business has totally changed for all but in name! Don’t go by the website, which is full of stock photos and lists a shaken, specialty coffee. Now it serves Vietnamese fast food fried bites, banh mi, and drinks, closed Mondays, which also hasn’t changed on their website. So unfortunately I arrived to use a FavePay voucher and it was closed, so didn’t try anything.

love the coffee here. dripped and shaken coffee which has a very unique taste to it !

the beef don is also really good!
Come and enjoy Video Gaming here at 5$ per hr . Drop ur kids and enjoy walking around stadium. Fun place to go in weekend kids will enjoy
Absolute unprofessional behaviour from the staff. Bad attitude and careless attitude. Wanted to rate Zero stars. Please avoid
